frontend/src/template/

# Real supplier list (business data: codes + prices). Kept out of git; the
# CSV-parser dry-run test uses runIf(existsSync) so it just skips when absent.
casone-stock-import.csv

# Markdown files — all .md treated as private notes (roadmaps, weekly
# planning, build logs, runbooks). The public-facing README at the repo
# root is the only exception; un-comment the `!README.md` line below if
# you want that one tracked. Everything else stays local-only.
*.md
# !README.md

# Boss / management-facing plain-English summary — keep private (also covered
# by *.md above; listed explicitly so it stays ignored even if .md is allowlisted).
lazy_task.md

# Self-directed feature planning — AI Help & System Assistant roadmap (private;
# also covered by *.md above, listed explicitly so it stays ignored even if .md
# is allowlisted).
ai_diagnostic_roadmap.md
